@page "/paragraph"
<PageTitle>Paragraph - Saascade Docs</PageTitle>

<h1>Paragraph</h1>

<main class="documentation">

    <section class="card">

        <h2>Overview</h2>

        <p class="subtitle">
            The <code>&lt;P&gt;</code> component renders a semantic <code>&lt;p&gt;</code>
            element with design-system-aware styling.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <h3>Basic Usage</h3>

        <pre><code>&lt;P&gt;This is a paragraph of text rendered through the Saascade component.&lt;/P&gt;</code></pre>

    </section>

